OL,3,CWoman says she's 'traumatised' by
OL,4,Cpartner's 'painful' hospital death
OL,6,FJohn Lamb's widow describes the moment
OL,7,Fhospital staff said her husband had
OL,8,Fdied
OL,10,FA woman from Cornwall says she has
OL,11,Fbeen left traumatised after her
OL,12,Fpartner of 47 years suffered a
OL,13,F"painful" and "undignified" death in
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FJoanna Cohen claims her partner, John
OL,17,FLamb, received an "unacceptable"
OL,18,Fstandard of care at Royal Cornwall
OL,19,FHospital after being admitted with
OL,20,Fheart and kidney failure in March.
