OL,3,CWoman says she's 'traumatised' by
OL,4,Cpartner's 'painful' hospital death
OL,6,FJoanna says there were a number of
OL,7,Fincidents in the five days before his
OL,8,Fdeath where the family felt his care
OL,9,Fwas not up to standard.
OL,11,FAccording to Joanna Cohen, nurses at
OL,12,FTreliske Hospital told her that her
OL,13,Fhusband was suffering muscular pain
OL,14,Fthat could be treated with Ibuprofen
OL,15,Fwhen he was in fact having a heart
OL,16,Fattack.
