OL,3,CWoman says she's 'traumatised' by
OL,4,Cpartner's 'painful' hospital death
OL,6,FThe hospital trust has apologised to
OL,7,FMs Cohen for any distress caused to
OL,8,Fthe family after her partner's death
OL,9,Fand told her that the relevant staff
OL,10,Fwould "receive training in
OL,11,Fcompassionate conversations and
OL,12,Fcommunications".
OL,14,FOver the course of the five days Mr
OL,15,FLamb spent in hospital, Ms Cohen said
OL,16,Fthere were multiple incidents that led
OL,17,Fup to his "undignified" death.
