OL,3,CWoman says she's 'traumatised' by
OL,4,Cpartner's 'painful' hospital death
OL,6,FShe explained: "It seems to me, from
OL,7,Fthe day that John got to the hospital,
OL,8,Fhe was just put in this bed, on this
OL,9,Fward, and left. No care whatsoever."
OL,11,FMs Cohen says that when her daughter
OL,12,Fcame from London to visit her father,
OL,13,Fshe found him "hanging off the bed
OL,14,Fwith his pyjama bottoms down his
OL,15,Fankles".
OL,17,FShe also told ITV News West Country
OL,18,Fthat before his death, Mr Lamb had
OL,19,Fbeen asking for painkillers for three
OL,20,Fhours without success.
