OL,3,CWoman says she's 'traumatised' by
OL,4,Cpartner's 'painful' hospital death
OL,6,FShe said: "I screamed for staff to
OL,7,Fcome again. There was a senior male
OL,8,Fnurse who said 'I'm preparing his
OL,9,FIbuprofen gel, he's got shoulder pain.
OL,10,FThat's what the pain in his back is.'
OL,11,FAnd I said 'It's not shoulder pain,
OL,12,Fit's his heart'.
OL,14,F"And I'm screaming at him because he's
OL,15,Fin a room outside, mixing this stuff
OL,16,Fup, taking his time, putting his
OL,17,Fgloves on. And I'm screaming at him,
OL,18,F'Can you hurry up and do something?'
OL,19,Fand he turned to me and said 'It's ok,
OL,20,Fhe's taking his last breaths. Just
OL,21,Fhold his hand'."
