OL,3,CWoman says she's 'traumatised' by
OL,4,Cpartner's 'painful' hospital death
OL,6,FMr Lamb has been described by his
OL,7,Ffamily as a "loving father and
OL,8,Fhusband" and a "very good man".
OL,10,FMs Cohen said: "It's hard. I promised
OL,11,FJohn on his deathbed that I wouldn't
OL,12,Flet him die in vain."
OL,14,FMs Cohen argued: "If they don't know
OL,15,Fcompassion, and how to look after
OL,16,Fsomeone who is seriously ill, then why
OL,17,Fare they in that job?"
