OL,6,FThe Royal Cornwall Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,7,Ftold Ms Cohen in its letter to her
OL,8,Fthat it had 'listened to her concerns
OL,9,Fand implemented the appropriate
OL,10,Factions'.
OL,12,FThe Royal Cornwall NHS Trust has been
OL,13,Fapproached by ITV News for a comment.
